com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.venues

Class VenueImageRequestExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.FileRequestExecutor
      • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.venues.VenueImageRequestExecutor

  • public class VenueImageRequestExecutor
extends FileRequestExecutor
    Request executor provided by VenuesApi. Use this class if you want to fetch venue's image file, for example: 
       
   KontaktCloud kontaktCloud = KontaktCloudFactory.create();
   FileData imageFile = kontaktCloud.venues().imageOf(venueID).execute();
